      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Contribute to the Atlas!",
          "textSize": "heading-one"
        }
      ],
      "align": "center"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "center",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "A letter from the author, Derrek Powell "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "",
          "textSize": "heading-three"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "textSize": "heading-three",
          "text": "I want your input and insight! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "This Atlas is an extension of my dissertation research, which focuses on the enregisterment of the reggaetón voice as an artistically identifiable singing style in Puerto Rico. However, I am not the linguistic authority on this subject, nor am I able to investigate every linguistic aspect of this performance style. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "If you are a scholar of reggaetón—in history, anthropology, political science, or linguistics—and you want to share your research with the Atlas as a way of helping to outline the reggaetón voice, please send me the following: "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "1. The Area of the Atlas you'd like to contribute to (phonology, lexicon, history, etc.) "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "2. What you'd like to contribute (an entry, additional information, a specific song feature, etc.) "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "If you would like to contribute an entry, please send me the following: "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "1. A brief introduction to the feature "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "2. A history of the feature "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "3. Any information you have about the feature's use in Puerto Rico "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "left",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "4. Information about how the feature shows up in reggaetón, complete with song example recommendations. "
        }
      ]
    },
